{"tid":1616012,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[十月三日] 我要做全香港抗爭者既窿","createTime":"2019-10-03T09:19:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T10:48:57.000Z","uid":24577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"af04ec3d098d2b0adf358ef2474a8bac92a8430a","tid":1616012,"uid":24577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:19:21.000Z","msg":"雖然我唔係前線 但係心理上 都好大壓力 每日都係到睇新聞睇直播 上twitter 上reddit<br />\n<br />\n望住香港 義士 抗爭者 好心痛 慢慢開始有depress<br />\n<br />\n但係我唔會咁就認輸！<br />\n<br />\n大家會有好多既原因 冇人傾訴 可能係唔可以亂講野 可能係屋企藍/紅<br />\n<br />\n但係呢啲野唔可以放係心由得佢慢慢侵蝕你 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你當我求下大家 同我傾計 有咩唔開心 同我講 我唔識你 所以都冇野可以威脅到你</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"1b3da093cb99f7e3e9d4709c0d490fd06b650e21","tid":1616012,"uid":24577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:20:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9ac989d63b697b3f6ee3c55854853f14f808157e","tid":1616012,"uid":24577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:21:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fee85949be5cc4470aeaea793a5ada464285bca4","tid":1616012,"uid":24577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:22:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0dc8335ce7254b520a7d1620d1d910774be0e03d","tid":1616012,"uid":24577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:47:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3939726a7ac97a7fece9b896491c308efdf7339b","tid":1616012,"uid":24577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:51:25.000Z","msg":"推到有人同我傾計"},{"pid":"67d9aad0be9b4a6065c7db667ffd4c537e84940e","tid":1616012,"uid":288272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:30:00.000Z","msg":"我報名入黎做窿 同大家齊上齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e5cfefc209d1afe4a52374e45c566817ed0cbf0","tid":1616012,"uid":24577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67d9aad0be9b4a6065c7db667ffd4c537e84940